COMMENT     THIRD PARTY ANNOTATION DATABASE: This TPA record uses data from
            DDBJ/EMBL/GenBank entry SRX081461
            The selective assembly was performed using GRAbB
            (https://github.com/b-brankovics/grabb). The following software
            versions were used: MIRA 4.0, seqtk 1.1-r91 and SPAdes 3.7.1 GRAbB
            was run on the read files using LT571433 (INSDC accession number)
            FASTA file as reference and using a modified version of
            external_skeleton.pl (from the GRAbB package). The overlapping ends
            of the assembled contigs were identified and trimmed manually to
            form a single circular sequence.
